From: IlMIE> 
To: 
Cc: 
Subject: RE: grand jury subpoena 
Date: Mon, 30 Sep 2019 23:25:20 +0000 
Attachments: 2019-08-11,_subpoena_to JD_Ameritrade.pdf 
To Whom it May Concern: 
Following up on the below, which transmitted the attached subpoena, TD Ameritrade is noncompliant with the subpoena, 
which required a response by the deadline of August 23, 2019. Additionally, we received a read receipt indicating that the 
email address ' read the below message the day after it was sent, on Monday, August 12, 
2019. 
Please advise whether TD Ameritrade intends to remedy its noncompliance and nonresponse to the subpoena or whether 
we will need to move to compel a response. 
thank you, 
Assistant U.S. Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
From: MMM>
Sent: Sunday, August 11, 2019 20:57 
To: 
Cc: 
Subject: RE: grand jury subpoena 
> 
Please see the attached service of legal process, in connection with a criminal grand jury investigation. 
thank you, 
Assistant U.S. Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
EFTA00021311
